---
title: Sweet ’n’ Spicy Apricot Chicken with Garlicky Green Beans & Chili-Roasted Carrots
description: “This meal is my JAM!” is what we’re pretty sure you’ll be saying after just one bite of these savory-sweet pork chops. Apricot jam blends with umami-rich ponzu and spicy Sriracha to make a tangy pan sauce with just enough heat to fire on all cylinders. You’ll serve it with chili-roasted carrots and garlicky roasted green beans. Flavorful, unique, memorable—this meal’s about to get totally stuck in your head.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-n-spicy-apricot-pork-chops-b6672f13.jpg
